[Steel Wind Strike.] 

You are able to move at extreme speed, seemingly teleporting to strike those around you. As an action, choose either a single target or any number of targets you can see within 30 feet. 

If you choose a single creature, you can make five melee weapon attacks against the creature.

You flourish the weapon used in the casting and then vanish to strike like the wind. Choose up to five creatures you can see within range (30 feet). Make a melee spell attack against each target. On a hit, a target takes 6d10 force damage.

You can then teleport to an unoccupied space you can see within 5 feet of one of the targets you hit or missed.

