#### Fueled By Pain
*3rd-level Mark of Vengeance feature*

<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

Your attacks are empowered by the wounds inflicted upon you. As your hit point total decreases, you gain an increas&shy;ing bonus to weapon damage rolls, as shown on the Pain Damage table. Temporary hit points do not count towards your hit point total for this ability.

##### Pain Damage Table
Bonus<br/>Damage | Current Hit Point Total
----|---
+0  | Hit point maximum
+1  | Less than hit point maximum
+2  | Less than half hit point maximum
+3  | 1 hit point

